ally we classify Dirac line nodes\nand Weyl line nodes to show in which types of mirror plane they can exist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2015 18:13:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 06:50:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 9 Aug 2015 05:34:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-18"}
