 MMC percolation was found in\nthe perpendicular plane and interpreted as onset of delamination caused by\nthermomechanical stress.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2015 19:59:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 11:36:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2015 23:14:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-07"}
