) of superhumps is also\nwell correlated with the estimated mass ratios. By using mass ratios from stage\nA superhumps and durarion of stage A, we have been able to identify best\ncandidates for period bouncers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 06:27:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 06:20:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-30"}
