re, the\ninference of a representative ejecta expansion rate, spectrum formation,\nblackbody fits and \"correction factors\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 14:30:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-09"}
